_header: Delivered the children of Israel out of thraldom and servage
_description: God’s assistance to the Israelites as they fled Egypt — three couplets in a Latin sermon

BodLatTheD1.First Lines:
delyueryd þe childre of israel out of thraldam &
                    seruageþorelk þe depe se he mad hem passage…
BodLatTheD1.Last Lines:
…He sente aungelys from heuen for hem to fyȝthAnd
                    schortly for þem all þat he myȝth
